    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add to your <strong>Wishlist</strong> to follow Central Bank!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316880/extras/c6b20312b84b8ba93a574e110d2ca0dd.poster.avif?t=1754983883\" width=364 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316880/extras/c6b20312b84b8ba93a574e110d2ca0dd.webm?t=1754983883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316880/extras/c6b20312b84b8ba93a574e110d2ca0dd.mp4?t=1754983883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Central Bank! The ultimate Central Bank simulator! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of the most fearsome weapon known to mankind: the key interest rate. As head of the central bank, you wield the power to make (or break) nations. Raise it, and watch markets crumble and riots erupt. Lower it, and brace yourself for an economy so hot it could melt steel.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316880/extras/b2de7709fa76cc3377106642218649a5.poster.avif?t=1754983883\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316880/extras/b2de7709fa76cc3377106642218649a5.webm?t=1754983883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316880/extras/b2de7709fa76cc3377106642218649a5.mp4?t=1754983883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the all-powerful shoes of a central banker, where you hold the world’s fate at your fingertips – literally. Central Bank is about weaving the fine line between euphoric prosperity and absolute chaos:<br><br> Too high, and the people revolt as homes become unaffordable, businesses collapse, and global unrest unfolds. Too low, and inflation runs rampant, society devolves into a free-for-all, and governments beg you to reverse course. Play god with the economy, manipulate prosperity, and watch as your every choice impacts millions. Will you be the savior of stability… or the architect of economic apocalypse?</p>",
